{"tid":1767010,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"21歲男周日彌敦道被截查搜出一枚汽油彈 今日提堂","createTime":"2019-12-03T04:07:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-03T05:21:56.000Z","uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"df1679a4166a0957a5893e3e66240533c9b97ed5","tid":1767010,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T04:07:24.000Z","msg":"警方周日（1日）晚上約10時半在彌敦道與豉油街交界巡邏期間，截停一名形迹可疑的男子。警員其後在他身上檢獲一枚汽油彈，經初步調查後，該名21歲姓黎本地男子涉嫌非法集結及藏有攻擊性武器被捕，現正被扣留調查。<br />\n<br />\n該名男子今日（2日）已被暫控一項藏有攻擊性武器罪，案件將於明日（3日）上午在九龍城裁判法院提堂。案件交由西九龍總區刑事部人員跟進。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20191202/s00001/1575301821067/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20191202%2Fs00001%2F1575301821067%2F&d=QAb612WS2prazXX2mE0KsXpsBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=92866352\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20191202%2Fs00001%2F1575301821067%2F&h=a66791d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20191202/s00001/1575301821067/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"535a6c563ea61eee31182cc1bea2fa814c33965e","tid":1767010,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T04:12:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7860e69ca83ea70f43691be144bbb3a174e046d3","tid":1767010,"uid":80931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T04:15:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />到場要醒目啲 跟人群走"},{"pid":"f726292a14345feace6928f397ce73b3e6ed19cf","tid":1767010,"uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T04:15:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"744b7104b00476f914ec0654673f71e15b43476